<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh vawlei ah a tum than lai, Nihin tum sual seh law, Thawnnak le
 dawtnak in pen awkah, Nihin rung tum sehlaw, A thimmi ngaknu lak awkah, A
 tlanhmi le tawlmi vialte, Vawlei khuazakip ah an um, Nihin rungtum sehlaw.

[C1]
   Thangthat ko ning, ka lung a lawmhter lai, Thangthat ko ning, Luchin
   ka chinh tikah, Thangthat ko ning, A lam remh awk caah, Thangthat ko
   ning, Jesuh a tum te lai.

[V2]
 Satan uknak a ciam zau te lai, Nihin va ciam seh law! Ngaihchiat
 tahhram a um ti lai lo, Nihin ah siseh law, Khrih ah a thimi an tho lai,
 Khrih ton awk van in an ngan lai, Khi sunpar zeitik kan hmuh lai, Nihin
 ah sisehlaw.

[C2]
   Thangthat ko ning, ka lung a lawmhter lai, Thangthat ko ning, Luchin
   ka chinh tikah, Thangthat ko ning, A lam remh awk caah, Thangthat ko
   ning, Jesuh a tum te lai.

[V3]
 Zumhfek le miding kan si lai maw? Nihin a tum ahcun, Tih loin,
 lunglawm in hngak u si, Nihin a rat ahcun, A rat lai hmelchunh a karh
 chin, Nichuahlei in ceu a lang cang, Hngak ko, a caan a nai deng cang,
 Nihin tum sual sehlaw.

[C3]
   Thangthat ko ning, ka lung a lawmhter lai, Thangthat ko ning, Luchin
   ka chinh tikah, Thangthat ko ning, A lam remh awk caah, Thangthat ko
   ning, Jesuh a tum te lai.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>NIHIN RUNG TUM SEHLAW CH167</title>
</song>